          "body": "Approach: Write the script with a real `argparse` help section, then implement the two functions exactly as the tests require. `is_eligible` checks labels first (fast path), then parses `Blocked-by:` lines and optionally resolves each blocker's state via the `gh` seam, short-circuiting on `virtually_closed`. `parse_closing_keywords` uses a single regex over GitHub's documented closing keyword set.\n\nPlan: docs/superpowers/plans/2026-05-17-gh-workflow-plan-a-pipeline.md#ship-issue-pick\nTracks: #55",
